OL,3,CNHS Trust tells visitors to stay away
OL,4,Cas it grapples with norovirus
OL,6,FPortsmouth Hospitals University NHS
OL,7,FTrust is urging visitors to stay away
OL,8,Ffrom the Queen Alexandra Hospital
OL,9,Funtil further notice, as it grapples
OL,10,Fwith norovirus cases.
OL,12,FThe Cosham-based hospital has asked to
OL,13,Fonly attend the hospital unless it is
OL,14,Fa medical emergency, to try and
OL,15,Fprevent the spread and to protect
OL,16,Fvulnerable patients, and its staff.
OL,18,FNorovirus is a winter vomiting disease
OL,19,Fthat can cause nausea, vomiting, or
OL,20,Fdiarrhoea.
