OL,3,CNHS Trust tells visitors to stay away
OL,4,Cas it grapples with norovirus
OL,6,FThe NHS Trust wants people to avoid
OL,7,Fvisiting the hospital if they have had
OL,8,Fsymptoms within the past 48 hours.
OL,10,FThe Trust has since released guidance
OL,11,Ffor anybody visiting the site, saying
OL,12,Fvisitors should wash their hands with
OL,13,Fsoap and water regularly when entering
OL,14,Fand exiting the ward and hospital.
OL,16,FIt also asks that appointments are
OL,17,Fattended alone or with one guest, and
OL,18,Fto limit the number of guests that
OL,19,Fjoin somebody attending the Emergency
OL,20,FDepartment.
