OL,4,Cas it grapples with norovirus
OL,6,F"Whilst we recognise how important
OL,7,Fvisitors are to the overall wellbeing
OL,8,Fof our patients, we must stop the
OL,9,Fspread of this virus in our hospitals
OL,10,Fto protect our vulnerable patients and
OL,11,Fstaff."
OL,13,FIf you need urgent medical advice
OL,14,Fplease contact NHS 111 online or call
OL,15,FNHS 111.
